text.section:
The Director shall:
Be responsible for the education of every child in a residential facility;
Ensure that the educational needs of every child in a residential facility are assessed in a timely manner;
Implement and administer the educational programs developed by the Council;
Meet with and advise the Council about education centers and educational programs and their outcomes; and
Consult with the Secretary and senior administrator of each residential facility about the operation of educational services for the program.
